    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Chocolate Almond/Walnut Smoothie"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<span><i class=\"fa fa-book\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/recipe-category/smoothies-and-drinks/\" rel=\"tag\">Smoothies and drinks</a></span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "April 9, 2016<span class=\"value-title\" title=\"2016-04-09\"></span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "Delicious! Great tasting chocolate smoothie, make it with some ice cubes and it’s almost like a soft serve ice cream, only much better tasting."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Prep: 5 min",
        "5 min 5 min",
        "Yields: 2 servings"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Ingredients"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 </span> <span class=\"name\">Banana</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">or 3-4 </span> <span class=\"name\">medjool dates, pitted</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 tbsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Cacao powder, raw</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/3 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">almonds or walnuts, activated and dehydrated if possible</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/2 tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Vanilla essence</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/2 tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Cinnamon, or to taste</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">Water (or less and add some ice cubes)</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Directions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>Put all ingredients in a blender and blend until smooth and creamy,"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>Pour into 2 glasses and serve immediately, but also keeps well in fridge for later."
    },
